OL,3,CCarol Clark: Man rearrested for murder
OL,4,C33 years after woman's death
OL,6,FA 69-year-old man from Gloucester has
OL,7,Fbeen rearrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmurder, 33 years after the death of
OL,9,FCarol Clark.
OL,11,FGloucestershire Police arrested the
OL,12,Fman at a house this morning (Tuesday
OL,13,F14 April) and he remains in police
OL,14,Fcustody.
OL,16,FThe man arrested today was previously
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of Carol's
OL,18,Fmurder in April 2023 and had remained
OL,19,Funder investigation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
