PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776280294
OL,3,CCarol Clark: Man rearrested for murder
OL,4,C33 years after woman's death
OL,6,FBut officers said they moved to detain
OL,7,Fhim for a second time for the same
OL,8,Foffence following 'a significant
OL,9,Fdevelopment' in their inquiry.
OL,11,FIn March 2026, officers investigating
OL,12,Fthe case released the last note Carol
OL,13,Fhad written before her death.
OL,15,FCarol was 32-years-old when her body
OL,16,Fwas found by a dog walker partially
OL,17,Fclothed in reeds and undergrowth at
OL,18,Fthe side of the Gloucester and
OL,19,FSharpness Canal on Sunday 28 March
OL,20,F1993.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776280294
OL,3,CCarol Clark: Man rearrested for murder
OL,4,C33 years after woman's death
OL,6,FShe had been strangled and her neck
OL,7,Fhad been broken.
OL,9,FDetective Chief Inspector Wayne Usher,
OL,10,Fhead of Gloucestershire Constabulary's
OL,11,FMajor Crime Investigation Team, said:
OL,12,F"Today's arrest is a significant
OL,13,Fdevelopment in our investigation to
OL,14,Fidentify Carol's killer and bring them
OL,15,Fto justice.
OL,17,F"For the past 33 years we have worked
OL,18,Fhard to solve this case, and we
OL,19,Fcontinue to leave no stone unturned.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776280294
OL,3,CCarol Clark: Man rearrested for murder
OL,4,C33 years after woman's death
OL,6,F"Last month, we issued a renewed
OL,7,Fappeal to the public for information
OL,8,Fabout Carol's death and I remain
OL,9,Fgrateful for the support both the
OL,10,Fmedia and the public continue to give
OL,11,Fus.
OL,13,F"Our thoughts remain with Carol's
OL,14,Ffamily at this time and we will
OL,15,Fcontinue to keep them informed about
OL,16,Fany further developments."
OL,18,FCarol's family have been made aware of
OL,19,Fthe development and are being
OL,20,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@ZO]
